---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import me from "../../assets/me.png";
import Contact from "../../components/Contact.astro";
const lang = "en";
const pageDescription = "An introduction to Haruta Watanabe's career.";
---

<BaseLayout description={pageDescription}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <header
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center mb-12 gap-8"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <Image
          src={me}
          alt="Haruta Watanabe"
          class="rounded-full w-24 h-24 object-cover shadow-md"
        />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">
            Haruta Watanabe (渡邉 朝太)
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1">
            Software Engineer / Data Science Enthusiast
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/resume_en.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        class="bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors inline-flex items-center flex-shrink-0"
        download
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-5 w-5 mr-2"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          ><path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Download PDF
      </a>
    </header>

    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <p>
        I am a law student with a strong interest in AI, data science, and
        software engineering.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have been honing my programming skills through professional roles,
        successfully replacing legacy ERP systems, and developing full-stack
        applications.
      </p>
      <p>
        My expertise includes building RESTful APIs, cross-platform mobile apps,
        and robust data validation systems. I am committed to leveraging my
        knowledge of Python, PostgreSQL, and machine learning principles to
        build scalable and efficient solutions.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>Professional Experience</h2>

      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3>Wakyu Co., Ltd. (May 2024 – Present)</h3>
        <p class="font-medium">Software Engineer (Part-time)</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Spearheading the modernization of a legacy ERP system for a printing
            company using Python, Django, and PostgreSQL.
          </li>
          <li>
            Engineered functionalities for a healthcare asset tracking platform
            using Java and PostgreSQL.
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed a protocol management system for local government-related
            projects using JavaScript to ensure transparency.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3>Howtelevision, Inc.</h3>
        <p class="font-medium">Software Engineer (Intern/Part-time)</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Designed and implemented RESTful APIs using FastAPI, leveraging
            asynchronous programming to handle concurrent user requests
            efficiently.
          </li>
          <li>
            Utilized Python Type Hints and Pydantic within FastAPI to ensure
            robust data validation and reduce runtime errors in production.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-6">
        <h3>
          Choco Next Year For Sure (Sole Proprietorship) (May 2025 – Present)
        </h3>
        <p class="font-medium">Founder & Lead Developer</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Founded a sole proprietorship and led a cross-functional team of
            developers to deliver full-stack solutions.
          </li>
          <li>
            Architected and deployed a cross-platform mobile application using
            Flutter and Firebase, managing the entire product lifecycle.:
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed high-performance web platforms using Astro and Tailwind
            CSS, optimizing for Core Web Vitals and SEO.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <hr />

      <h2>Educational Background</h2>
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3>Chuo University | Tokyo, Japan</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Bachelor of Laws (LL.B.)</strong> | Expected Mar 2028
        </p>
        <p>
          GPA: 3.48/4.0 (Upward Trend: 3.61/4.0 in the most recent academic
          year)
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3>The University of Tokyo, Matsuo Iwasawa Laboratory | Remote</h3>
        <p>
          <strong
            >GCI (Global Consumer Intelligence) Data Science Program</strong
          > | Mar 2026
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Completed intensive data science and machine learning curriculum
            using Python.
          </li>
          <li>
            Mastered predictive modeling and data analysis using NumPy, Pandas,
            and Scikit-learn.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3>Harvard University (via edX) | Remote</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>CS50x: Introduction to Computer Science</strong> | Jan 2026
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Validated foundational knowledge in Data Structures, Algorithms, and
            Memory Management.
          </li>
          <li>
            Completed complex problem sets in C, Python, SQL, and JavaScript.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <hr />

      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Programming Languages:</strong> Python (Proficient), Java, Dart,
          JavaScript, SQL (PostgreSQL), C, HTML/CSS
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Frameworks & Technologies:</strong> Django, FastAPI, Flutter, Firebase,
          Astro, Tailwind CSS, Node.js, NumPy, Pandas, Scikit-learn
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Tools & Platforms:</strong> Git, GitHub, GitLab, Linux (WSL), Docker,
          Google Cloud/Firebase
        </li>
      </ul>
      <hr />
      <Contact lang={lang} />
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-2xl font-bold mb-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-2;
  }
  .prose h3 {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold;
  }
</style>
